Her : Thought you said you was taking me to Cuba ?
Him : Facts. Zona de Cuba.. in the Bronx < SWIPE > 
[shot by @thedonlikecheadle]
#HungryForCultureTV

1. Misco-Cuba-cation 
2. Walk you thru the kitchen like a Good Fella 
3. I know the Owner, met the Chef 
4.  Red Snapper for the Rapper
5. Cigar.. Food.. Links.. all Cuban
6. When the smoke clears I’ll be right here 
7. Old Schools from the 50’s
8. The elevator is up.. but not stuck 
9. Goyard Cigar Case 
10. J Balvin X Jordan 1
